**SUSTAINABLE TECHNOLOGY ADOPTION SCORE: 66/100**

Technology Adoption: 17/25  
Innovation Leadership: 18/25  
Measurable Impact: 13/25  
Future Strategy: 11/15  
Industry Position: 7/10

Summary (short): Huntington Ingalls Industries (HII) has moved from basic sustainability disclosure toward active deployment of energy‑efficiency and operations technologies (LED, HVAC upgrades, electrification of small fleet, ISO 14001 sites), organizational programs (Climate Transition Plan, Sustainability Reports) and targeted R&D/partnership activity (unmanned systems, DOE environmental contracts, AI partnerships). The company shows measurable Scope 1/2 reductions (~10% year‑over‑year 2022→2023) but has not yet disclosed complete Scope 3 targets. Overall, HII is a solid mid‑tier performer on sustainable technology adoption and innovation for the shipbuilding/defense sector — progressive and credible but not yet a sector leader on breakthrough low‑carbon tech or comprehensive value‑chain decarbonization.

Detailed findings, evidence and scoring justification

Technology Adoption (17/25) — What sustainable technologies has HII implemented?
- Documented site and operations measures (2022–2025): LED lighting replacements, HVAC upgrades, new roofing to improve energy performance, solar deployments and electrification of mobile equipment and small utility vehicles (Newport News—about one‑third of small motorized carts now electric) — applied at scale across shipyards and facilities [hii](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQEK7slEyV4TvNiKTmLvH-DoOu5u6LpNGVLNPqJy23DmVAs9ucrt2fV5ey5qj8E25uod26IUlW0UheAU15mGn7nTkTC2mNUXXeA9r6i3361Lw9JNh-4fDczsywNPxU9hns3mObOaN26_p4Ho-CPfcbwRvAI8OxdHbrbCyclwIawdOJT4J5VgBA==) [hii](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQEGd8xwv1TLgjx4WsdBs1fvcB5uL1o8k1LF85ZHfrxaF1LNqoakdZUC7tQcAaQ0tiRDsdhW5v7qSXF0LU89wESRSPiOEHs7WJaTNkQ2zUzgbTiDquaF59oiZFjugPMTQFaJ82WcIYQf3vv5NQ_-7QKqFv8_LW-GO8jpOL6SK8ZQ2hh8y3Qg9MRO1iKZPoRwtps=) [hii](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQEK7slEyV4TvNiKTmLvH-DoOu5u6LpNGVLNPqJy23DmVAs9ucrt2fV5ey5qj8E25uod26IUlW0UheAU15mGn7nTkTC2mNUXXeA9r6i3361Lw9JNh-4fDczsywNPxU9hns3mObOaN26_p4Ho-CPfcbwRvAI8OxdHbrbCyclwIawdOJT4J5VgBA==).
- Energy/GHG management and certifications: ISO 14001 for key facilities and active energy/GHG tracking and reporting (Scope 1 & 2 baselines and annual disclosure) [hii](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQEK7slEyV4TvNiKTmLvH-DoOu5u6LpNGVLNPqJy23DmVAs9ucrt2fV5ey5qj8E25uod26IUlW0UheAU15mGn7nTkTC2mNUXXeA9r6i3361Lw9JNh-4fDczsywNPxU9hns3mObOaN26_p4Ho-CPfcbwRvAI8OxdHbrbCyclwIawdOJT4J5VgBA==) [q4cdn](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQEZ_09KQssuTnN7ld5_KUMp83JIMEJ6JyXPrmN-lq2xsxGOpfBmDZSMhfMf3HEd727jcEHEJSY9efat0jQiRF4bnPqxnFpqlX7PRPIFaqW_Hn2Pk9z5Lxk-rFaL1noXGtcUpuM_lvUpbvKff6owWTX9gHAkhdbMM_c6i5Cl17Ak_WcqFFsb5u03af0=).
- Operational practices: leak detection/tracking at Newport News, waste diversion / material reuse & recycling programs, and increased use of data to optimize HVAC/lighting [hii](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQEK7slEyV4TvNiKTmLvH-DoOu5u6LpNGVLNPqJy23DmVAs9ucrt2fV5ey5qj8E25uod26IUlW0UheAU15mGn7nTkTC2mNUXXeA9r6i3361Lw9JNh-4fDczsywNPxU9hns3mObOaN26_p4Ho-CPfcbwRvAI8OxdHbrbCyclwIawdOJT4J5VgBA==) [hii](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQGCRrAkpuCkGzvdBY7yqR41eT6rO_0bzJ3qmNeM4Zs2dkP23ORMmVc1FO7sUFNBBMho45szjOqnY1_ivM5s1LhzMh9SOL_KftG3IAuAVV7RUhOj5yQvQB0M58HyCPDPUXcZK5pU-lCxDnu2kvTn3QAODO85en7xIv6WYKUr0U99bqEneaKS5VM=).
- Nuclear shipbuilding and nuclear & environmental services: HII is one of the U.S. firms building nuclear‑powered naval vessels and operates a Nuclear & Environmental Group supporting DOE clean‑up — relevant to low‑carbon energy systems and environmental services rather than direct corporate renewable power generation [hii](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQEK7slEyV4TvNiKTmLvH-DoOu5u6LpNGVLNPqJy23DmVAs9ucrt2fV5ey5qj8E25uod26IUlW0UheAU15mGn7nTkTC2mNUXXeA9r6i3361Lw9JNh-4fDczsywNPxU9hns3mObOaN26_p4Ho-CPfcbwRvAI8OxdHbrbCyclwIawdOJT4J5VgBA==) [ans](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQE8Uw6TMkn1ah_UEnHygBck9uDkz_oF8uD3tDsLXeV3TT_31gQtXtU_IuVUDY-y8kk6z7l1HPjUKZnouAqggIWC-yDEkFzd4PAWwCizq44hVvLx9mxIB5HVQfMqTr_YPr1nfUh5jzZ_pQ2Z6o7JpKFXk52Gl1qc-nTDUKtdpaGQVZ_z6vtctV7caoGobw==) [hii](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQGbMBEsw1jgad8EwMnhEhctBW7LWaUjRCROfmNYsAKhT4NuIULWJsd_okFWKw0xwl-FbIhuFj6kmHg4kVkq350a2MMRgO7d99mtjoB8Qt3c29FXNT3fyNs0gYpNHKutNxiO7P3bCrogVQ4iTIy6N0DJ4qhdDYh_ecA2R6SD1nYJFkfDj91aUQAsVVr5bhjp80BUNcjpXLLL9BCkRlRcENC8uMFPuRtBXLtyyAfFDIKyOs0=).

Why 17/25: HII has implemented several tangible sustainable technologies across operations and holds formal environmental management certifications. However, most deployments are conventional energy‑efficiency and electrification measures (important and scalable), with fewer documented large‑scale breakthrough deployments (e.g., onsite utility‑scale renewables, industrial CCS at HII facilities) in public disclosures 2022–2025. Sources: [hii](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQEK7slEyV4TvNiKTmLvH-DoOu5u6LpNGVLNPqJy23DmVAs9ucrt2fV5ey5qj8E25uod26IUlW0UheAU15mGn7nTkTC2mNUXXeA9r6i3361Lw9JNh-4fDczsywNPxU9hns3mObOaN26_p4Ho-CPfcbwRvAI8OxdHbrbCyclwIawdOJT4J5VgBA==) [hii](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQEGd8xwv1TLgjx4WsdBs1fvcB5uL1o8k1LF85ZHfrxaF1LNqoakdZUC7tQcAaQ0tiRDsdhW5v7qSXF0LU89wESRSPiOEHs7WJaTNkQ2zUzgbTiDquaF59oiZFjugPMTQFaJ82WcIYQf3vv5NQ_-7QKqFv8_LW-GO8jpOL6SK8ZQ2hh8y3Qg9MRO1iKZPoRwtps=) [q4cdn](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQEZ_09KQssuTnN7ld5_KUMp83JIMEJ6JyXPrmN-lq2xsxGOpfBmDZSMhfMf3HEd727jcEHEJSY9efat0jQiRF4bnPqxnFpqlX7PRPIFaqW_Hn2Pk9z5Lxk-rFaL1noXGtcUpuM_lvUpbvKff6owWTX9gHAkhdbMM_c6i5Cl17Ak_WcqFFsb5u03af0=).

Innovation Leadership (18/25) — R&D, pilots and partnerships
- Active initiatives and partnerships: HII runs a Sustainability Program (launched 2022) and publishes annual Sustainability Reports (2024, 2025) aligned to GRI/SASB/TCFD; it is developing a Climate Transition Plan and collaborating with partners (including AI/analytics partnerships like C3 AI) to improve operational efficiency [hii](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQEXYZZ1T243HubQvGzv2gkNRLW8njClObEV4RGBrf8dvri9rxnesfEjDJZQ84xmBRYPzNIPNoETTRCAnSzIyP4Vr7l-k5mmg5a6IQgVK7B7yYo3JE_o0bwESgDX83IcMXHAw6ZM4WEKvlqPd65Y__ZeDJkedVr0uOs0Kpis86444O0JLm22y10=) [hii](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQEeWPtQsitA2GW2oV5HTmY7zgfBYKeb81-aExjyvKucMjdfq2SwY8LZPo0i9E3pPbS6sc_KN1ZZ46mo-wg87m5MN19CYzRE6BnUTF1mkKS6DpUfE_2DEFZuyrLA5ejiV_v8hR49ctcHmjj4IEG0vQfkmkbFxCAZn58u-wxXMoZSEV5oibFFYXC9uogXnz22P9BsGpDP2w==) [ainvest](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQFRM9ZnMk156N62jSpdNkYovM8ByrRe28uvvi1kkMNq09r1aP7eRnvAz3jw3o9Qn31EXUVNObcjDOnNphhcsNKanhmM2SergzFoyzlk_orMsBZ9KDe2Mnnjbmd-jW3yOLRLzlqvq2ubnGHDYlLWCp8UqMT0JwPLru5xzHPGoNIbbiJkwcdTRL2lizFmjk-TdmhlczAaJSQYeWd52iVm0eBWqWYsafA3jIPKk1SM).
