- Other quantifiable operational benefits: safety improvements (Total Case Rate reduction), waste diversion where feasible, electrification of a portion of small vehicles, and stated throughput/cost efficiency gains from advanced manufacturing pilots (no single large publicly disclosed resource‑saving >25% in operations) [hii](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQHZ1PR3wydiTkqep4UFlP78wjSSfdvfCedJ2exfImrml1GKf6i6_eWuwgjeXiXOZyHSogTqMryZonQIx6pShP05JSaqMaGLB34OC2ceIsa8GKH67osbu9QaSoE9M1UbKRM95gtAm9XffVJTt1brxlLwkRJgUd8RhQz1rb5LesecWepptVPZarAo_IistO2Ser7H) [hii](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQGCRrAkpuCkGzvdBY7yqR41eT6rO_0bzJ3qmNeM4Zs2dkP23ORMmVc1FO7sUFNBBMho45szjOqnY1_ivM5s1LhzMh9SOL_KftG3IAuAVV7RUhOj5yQvQB0M58HyCPDPUXcZK5pU-lCxDnu2kvTn3QAODO85en7xIv6WYKUr0U99bqEneaKS5VM=).
- Scope 3: HII had not fully evaluated or set Scope 3 targets as of 12/31/2023 — a material gap given much of shipbuilding emissions can reside in upstream/downstream categories [hii](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQHHGr02dAGb0vMyfY8lnaxhMoYwKtl4Ktb_HfEdZC1Rxm5Bcjz8bh_RG1zIlO3VA1v4dptqzMIgMVyQKUZ3YLliZp4H6X8pVJCxoYHCLTLuMhMztoZ13QB9n-dNoUiav77VNgZIwVWZcjdyUxxI66XC4U11Hrn_omD1BctlpafoBXhZCsrY8Lz2GVK7d1QHg29Zig==) [cloudfront](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQEYHZGxdw6ow3FZ2NlR9zq97-8mPTaV623xxsZuFx1nwjeomQfDTtevBPPRyC5rG8AjURnDOFGQ0idfSx1oj5PNSyTmNo_7wwVGi5BcEZNbVUB0rHiD_0bHyoZrAvFa6AR14p_dkYZ8pnJX3eQYRyO4EHrXwRMDNOktj2QWxhWwOvE85gPa0HMXUfOMKe7r1ay40CIVr5t4ew==).

Why 13/25: The company documents real, measurable reductions in Scope 1 & 2 in 2023 vs 2022 (≈10% total reduction), which places measurable performance in the “moderate” band (10–25% improvements). However, the absence of comprehensive Scope 3 accounting/targets and the limited scale of transformational resource reductions (none >25% documented) prevent a higher score. Sources: [hii](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQHHGr02dAGb0vMyfY8lnaxhMoYwKtl4Ktb_HfEdZC1Rxm5Bcjz8bh_RG1zIlO3VA1v4dptqzMIgMVyQKUZ3YLliZp4H6X8pVJCxoYHCLTLuMhMztoZ13QB9n-dNoUiav77VNgZIwVWZcjdyUxxI66XC4U11Hrn_omD1BctlpafoBXhZCsrY8Lz2GVK7d1QHg29Zig==) [hii](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQFNmgU3scE-PqClWTcCvZiiKu11zW5rxLeI_Yx6IbTTBrIvUZcTF3VRE1wLi7DvyhyDOWx_Y_peIYVT_FtpCOhc_9_JX-ktpZZZ3itZYbfkMxmZdu4THNuatK8dDqUqytNxC8YNP4m8hNX4ylapB6FoOgT_-6Uue5p1WU5QQfEeDRbIgVSr3MMR9Zcsa_wbv8cU8GV-GgHSamimFJ-VEjmI66KqyzI=) [hii](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQE4PPLnfrsd0F1vaxJwSRhN7yTp6-0T32S9Ds4kFS83zwfKVPokrcJOjv3yASzwIGH4qq-AK6b99MX0YKnGY_fsNfcIivlROrBgYpZSNkPOeU_mSaIOa6VF2CEFEHt-R0HsUs8EPXxKA8zGSFTRwxg4PMRykB7isnToZ9Xx_M0D_UV9F5sjhB8=).

